1 Ekayā eva jihvayā pūrvam mama daṣṭam,
2 Tena me eka eva gaṇḍaḥ anyaś ca rañjitaḥ,
3 Tataś ca auṣadham mama punar ārogyam ādadau;

10 Tatrārdharātriḥardhadivasamapi
11 Āsīt, yataḥ mama darśanam alpam agre agamat;
12 Atha aham śuśrāva mahān nādaḥ śṛṅgātkṛtaḥ,

19 Alpataram tatra śiraḥ praṇayām āsam,
20 yatra me adarśanta bahu udgatāḥ prastara-śṛṅgāḥ;
21 tataḥ aham uvāca: "Bhagavan, kim ayam deśaḥ?".

25 Tvam eva drakṣyasi, yadi tatra tvam yogaṃ karoṣi,
26 katham indriyāṇi dūrato mohayanti;
27 atas tvam ātmānam eva adhikaṃ codaya.

37 tathā sthūlām andhakārāyuktāṃ vāyum vibhidya,
38 punaḥ punaḥ tīram abhimukham āgacchan,
39 mohaḥ mama apasarati bhayam ca vardhate;

52 Yadyapi sā gajānāṃ tathā timīṅgīlānāṃ
53 na paścāttāpaṃ karoti, yaḥ sūkṣmatayā paśyati,
54 sāṃ nyāyyatarāṃ viśiṣṭatarāṃ ca māṃ manyate;

58 Tasya vaktram dīrghaṃ sthūlaṃ ca me abhāsata
59 Yathā Romasthitā San-Pīṭara-śṛṅgaḥ,
60 Tathā ca anyāny asthi tasyānusāreṇa āsīt;

64 Trīṇi Frisīyāṇi vyartham abhimānaṃ kuryuḥ;
65 Yataḥ aṣṭādaśa hasta-parimāṇam tasya dehasya adhaḥ-bhāgam asmābhiḥ dṛṣṭam,
66 Yatra puruṣaḥ vastraṃ baṇḍhanena yojayati.

76 Tataḥ sa uvāca mama: "Sā svayam eva ātmānam abhiyuktaṃ karoti;
77 ayam Nimbrottaḥ asti yasya pāpa-buddhyā
78 eka eva bhāṣā jagati na prayujyate.

79 Tyaktvā tam na vaktavyam asmābhiḥ mithyā;
80 yataḥ tasya sarvaḥ śabdaḥ
81 yathā anyasya svaḥ, yaḥ na kenāpi jñāyate.

94 Fialte nāma asya, yā ca mahāparīkṣāḥ cakāra
95 yadā daityaḥ devān bibhayayām āsuḥ;
96 bāhū yau tayā prayuktāv anavaratam calataḥ.

124 Naḥ Tityam vā Tivram vā gantum kārayāḥ:
125 Ayaṃ tatra yācitam prayacchati;
126 Atas tvam namas kuru mā ca vaktram vikṛṣṭam kuru.

133 Virgilio, yadā ātmanam gṛhītam anubabhūva,
134 mama abravīt: "Iha āgaccha, yathā aham tvām gṛhṇāmi";
135 tataḥ cakāra yathā ekaḥ puṭaḥ āvām abhavatām.

142 Api tu mṛdulamūlena yad bhakṣayati
143 Luciferam saha Yūdayā sa no nyavedayat;
144 na ca, tathā namitaḥ, tatra sthitim cakāra,
